    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="2020-5-14拍摄秦岭云"><a href="#2020-5-14拍摄秦岭云" class="headerlink" title="2020.5.14拍摄秦岭云"></a>2020.5.14拍摄秦岭云</h1><hr><p>云来山更佳，云去山如画。<br>山因云晦明，云共山高下。<br>——张养浩《双调·雁儿落兼得令》<br><a href="https://postimg.cc/vcNg4P0N" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/vcNg4P0N/DSC1337.jpg" alt="DSC1337"/></a> <a href="https://postimg.cc/9rMwF3Y9" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/9rMwF3Y9/DSC1337-2.jpg" alt="DSC1337-2"/></a><br/><br/><br><a href="https://postimg.cc/jDnWPz9d" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/jDnWPz9d/DSC1337-3.jpg" alt="DSC1337-3"/></a> <a href="https://postimg.cc/9zcqKw4J" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/9zcqKw4J/DSC1338.jpg" alt="DSC1338"/></a><br/><br/><br><a href="https://postimg.cc/qt8zZp4P" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/qt8zZp4P/DSC1338-Pano.jpg" alt="DSC1338-Pano"/></a> <a href="https://postimg.cc/hJFXrXW8" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/hJFXrXW8/DSC1341.jpg" alt="DSC1341"/></a><br/><br/><br><a href="https://postimg.cc/47snDj3m" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/47snDj3m/DSC1342.jpg" alt="DSC1342"/></a> </p>]]></content>
    
    
    
