    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="2020-3-20拍摄海棠花"><a href="#2020-3-20拍摄海棠花" class="headerlink" title="2020.3.20拍摄海棠花"></a>2020.3.20拍摄海棠花</h1><hr><p>细雨初怜湿翠裳，新晴特地试红妆。<br>无人会得东风意，春色都将付海棠。——【宋】杨万里《海棠坞》<br><a href="https://postimg.cc/6yphjv9c" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/6yphjv9c/DSC1042.jpg" alt="DSC1042"/></a> <a href="https://postimg.cc/NLS0Shtn" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/NLS0Shtn/DSC1043.jpg" alt="DSC1043"/></a><br/><br/><br><a href="https://postimg.cc/0zqy5pbd" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/0zqy5pbd/DSC1044.jpg" alt="DSC1044"/></a> <a href="https://postimg.cc/5YktfTC6" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/5YktfTC6/DSC1045.jpg" alt="DSC1045"/></a><br/><br/><br><a href="https://postimg.cc/qgPkQ8XV" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/qgPkQ8XV/DSC1046.jpg" alt="DSC1046"/></a> <a href="https://postimg.cc/CnF4VZbF" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/CnF4VZbF/DSC1047.jpg" alt="DSC1047"/></a><br/><br/><br><a href="https://postimg.cc/YGNxVNGn" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/YGNxVNGn/DSC1048.jpg" alt="DSC1048"/></a> <a href="https://postimg.cc/Xp1kTYqb" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Xp1kTYqb/DSC1052.jpg" alt="DSC1052"/></a><br/><br/></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
